previous_texts: p: Contact us to learn more!
p: We look forward to making The Tyler your new home!

p: Come experience the new stylish and sophisticated look of the historic former East Haven High School. Choose from beautifully planned one and two bedroom apartment homes featuring tall ceilings, over-sized windows, fully appointed kitchens with rich walnut wood cabinets and slate-look flooring.  Residents of The Tyler will enjoy the convenience of an on site laundry care center plus an impressive amenity package including fitness center, lounge with hosted social activities, a crafting room, indoor and outdoor gathering areas, dedicated on-site parking and on-site management.

p: Nestled in a residential neighborhood, The Tyler is East Haven’s newest apartment community for adults age 55+.  A handsome landmark that once served as the East Haven High School and is now listed on the National Register of Historic Places, has been reintroduced as modern apartment living available now!  Learn more about our innovative community here.

p: We look forward to making The Tyler your new home!

p: Come experience the new stylish and sophisticated look of the historic former East Haven High School. Choose from beautifully planned one and two bedroom apartment homes featuring tall ceilings, over-sized windows, fully appointed kitchens with rich walnut wood cabinets and slate-look flooring.  Residents of The Tyler will enjoy the convenience of an on site laundry care center plus an impressive amenity package including fitness center, lounge with hosted social activities, a crafting room, indoor and outdoor gathering areas, dedicated on-site parking and on-site management.

p: Nestled in a residential neighborhood, The Tyler is East Haven’s newest apartment community for adults age 55+.  A handsome landmark that once served as the East Haven High School and is now listed on the National Register of Historic Places, has been reintroduced as modern apartment living available now!  Learn more about our innovative community here.

previous_texts:
h1: Projekte
an KiTa´s, Schulen und Firmen
p: Komm´ auf uns zu - wir begrüßen Dich herzlich!

p: Wir freuen uns immer wieder auf Menschen, die den afrikanischen Kontinent lieben und respektieren und ebenso auf Menschen, die die "Anderswelt" kennen lernen möchten oder mal "über den Tellerrand schauen" wollen.
next_texts: p: Wir lieben, was wir sind und freuen uns, ein Teil Deiner Interessen zu sein!
p: Wir leiten, präsentieren und organisieren alles rund um die Westafrikanische Trommel-Kunst und Kultur – und das leidenschaftlich gerne!
h4: Afrikanisches Trommeln für alle Ansprüche
p: Sehr gut geführte Kurse, Workshops und Projekte

previous_texts: p: Komm´ auf uns zu - wir begrüßen Dich herzlich!

p: Wir freuen uns immer wieder auf Menschen, die den afrikanischen Kontinent lieben und respektieren und ebenso auf Menschen, die die "Anderswelt" kennen lernen möchten oder mal "über den Tellerrand schauen" wollen.
p: Darüber hinaus zeigt die SeneGALerie auch ihr Gesicht in Senegal und bietet autentischen Afrika-Urlaub im "LIM-Camp" in Somone (an der Petit Côte) für Abenteurer, Individualisten und Backpacker.
p: Liebhaber der afrikanischen Boho & Hippie Mode bekommen hier durch die kreative Hand von Veronika Sow einzigartige Unikate, die sich sehen lassen können.
p: SeneGALerie steht auch für das Handwerk an und mit der Natur: Professionelle Djembé-Reparaturen werden durch die Meisterhand von Ousmane Sow durchgeführt.

next_texts: p: Die SeneGALerie ist im Jahr 2001 aus einer Idee heraus über Nacht entstanden. Sie präsentiert eine kreative Mischung mit Inhalten der tief verwurzelten westafrikanischen Trommel-Kunst und Musik-Kultur durch Trommel Kurse, Trommel Workshops, Tanz Workshops mit choreographischen Tanzelementen aus dem Leben Afrikas (kein Sabar Tanz!), Trommel Projekte, Auftritte und spezielle Highlights und Veranstaltungen.

p: Liebhaber der afrikanischen Boho & Hippie Mode bekommen hier durch die kreative Hand von Veronika Sow einzigartige Unikate, die sich sehen lassen können.

Confirmation de présence

                                                        Déclenchement de l'alerte si le protégé n'a pas confirmé sa présence à échéance d'une durée pré-définie. Si la tâche du travailleur isolé le nécessite, le smartphone peut donc être configuré de manière à, solliciter régulièrement le protégé pour qu'il confirme manuellement sa présence.

p: 
                                    Désigné sous les termes DATI ou EPI, le dispositif innovant Eazen se compose d'une application pour smartphone capable de détecter automatiquement un incident et de lancer une alerte, puis, d'autre part, d'un gestionnaire en ligne centralisant en temps réels toutes les informations destinées à faciliter l'intervention de secours si nécessaire.

p: 
Eazen s'adresse aux travailleurs isolés et donc à toutes personnes (chefs d'entreprise, responsables RH...) faisant de la sécurité de leurs collaborateurs, une priorité.
h1: Ange Gardien 4.0, Eazen veille et protège vos collaborateurs, travailleurs isolés.

p: Vos informations personnelles ne feront l'objet d'aucun suivi lors de votre visite sur notre site. Cependant, en vue de respecter vos préférences, nous devrons utiliser un petit cookie pour que nous n'ayons pas à vous les redemander.
next_texts:
p:

h3: 
					Pluralité et performance des modes de détection

alt: L'application mobile sert á détecter une situation anormale et envoi une alerte au veilleur en charge du protégé concerné afin qu'il puisse intervenir rapidement.

attrs.alt: L'application mobile sert á détecter une situation anormale et envoi une alerte au veilleur en charge du protégé concerné afin qu'il puisse intervenir rapidement.

previous_texts:
h3: 
                                                Le superviseur administre et configure intégralement la solution Eazen.

p: Le veilleur est une personne de confiance conjointement désignée par le travailleur isolé et le superviseur. S'il reçoit une alerte, c'est lui qui s'occupera de recontacter son protégé et, si besoin, d'appeler les secours pour lui venir en aide en un minimum de temps ! Plusieurs veilleurs peuvent être désignés. En plus d'alerter en temps réel le veilleur par sms, e-mail et via l'interface de gestion, Eazen fournit un rapport détaillé sur l'anomalie enregistrée, la géo-localisation du travailleur isolé en danger et celle de tous les secours environnants.

h3: 
                                                Le veilleur reçoit l'alerte de son protégé.

p: Son téléphone détecte une situation anormale (absence de mouvement prolongée, chute, choc, perte de verticalité ou déclenchement manuel volontaire) et envoie automatiquement une alerte au veilleur.Un compte à rebours est déclenché dès que l'incident est détecté par le smartphone,  laissant ainsi l'opportunité au protégé d'annuler manuellement, si nécessaire, le lancement de l'alerte.

h3: 
                                                Votre protégé (le travailleur isolé) est en danger ?
next_texts: p: 4 modes de détection entièrement paramétrables, en plus du déclenchement manuel possible de l'alerte :

p: 
Chutes ou chocs

                                                        Déclenchement de l'alerte lorsque la smartphone subit une chute ou une projection.

p: 
Perte de verticalité

                                                        Déclenchement de l'alerte lorsque le smartphone reste à l'horizontal pendant une durée pré-définie.

p: 
Immobilisme

                                                        Déclenchement de l'alerte lorsque le smartphone ne capte aucun mouvement pendant une durée pré-définie.

p: 
Confirmation de présence

                                                        Déclenchement de l'alerte si le protégé n'a pas confirmé sa présence à échéance d'une durée pré-définie. Si la tâche du travailleur isolé le nécessite, le smartphone peut donc être configuré de manière à, solliciter régulièrement le protégé pour qu'il confirme manuellement sa présence.

attrs.alt: Creatieve en innovatieve beursstand voor CEBEO
attrs.title: Bij Expo Z verzorgen we jouw stand voor een succesvolle beursdeelname

previous_texts: p: Creating spaces to connect people

p: Met meer dan 25 jaar ervaring in standenbouw haalt Expo Z meer uit je beursstand, pop-up of event. Jouw ideeën en wensen in combinatie met onze expertise, passie en vakmanschap resulteert in bijzondere creaties waar beleving voorop staat.
h1: Standenbouw met beleving op maat
next_texts: p: Wij creëren creatieve en unieke standen voor een succesvolle beursdeelname. Als standenbouwer ontwikkelen we in samenspraak met de klant een ontwerp, waarna we overgaan tot de volledige ontwikkeling en opbouw van de stand. U kan bij ons terecht voor standenbouw van A tot Z.

p: Openen jullie binnenkort en pop-up winkel of organiseren jullie een evenement? Wij vertalen jouw merkidentiteit naar een totale inrichting van een tijdelijke ruimte waarin jullie mensen samenbrengen.
h2: Een vlotte samenwerking in 3 stappen

alt: Detail van de beursstand voor Powerplus

attrs.alt: Detail van de beursstand voor Powerplus
attrs.title: Wij dragen perfectionisme hoog in het vaandel en beschikken over een eigen atelier waar een hoge afwerkingsgraad wordt nagestreefd.

previous_texts: p: Heb je een specifiek idee of wens? Shoot! Wij houden van een uitdaging. De creatieve mogelijkheden zijn namelijk eindeloos. Als jij het kan bedenken, kunnen wij het maken. Na 2 tot 3 weken kan je rekenen op een prachtig ontwerp op maat.
p: Onze interieurarchitecten gaan na het kennismakingsgesprek aan de slag om een passend ontwerp te maken. Elk ontwerp van Expo Z is een ontwerp op maat, want elke klant is uniek.
p: Jij vertelt, wij luisteren, adviseren en informeren. Een gek idee of helemaal carte blanche? Kom maar op! Bij Expo Z houden we van een creatieve uitdaging.

p: Na een telefoongesprek of e-mail maken we een vrijblijvende afspraak. We zitten graag met jou aan tafel om meer te weten te komen over jouw project, je visie, budget, timing, huisstijl en alle andere essentiële details.
next_texts: p: Een team van schrijnwerkers gaat hierna aan de slag in het atelier om het finale ontwerp te realiseren. Wij dragen perfectionisme hoog in het vaandel en beschikken over een eigen atelier waar een hoge afwerkingsgraad wordt nagestreefd.
p: Diezelfde schrijnwerkers transporteren hierna jouw goederen naar de juiste locatie en ook de plaatsing nemen zij voor hun rekening. Sit down & relax, wij doen de rest!
h3: Succesvolle en langdurige samenwerking tussen Nipro en standenbouwer Expo Z

previous_texts: p: Enkelte strømleverandører tilbyr også app-løsninger som viser hvor mye av den egenproduserte strømmen du benytter til eget forbruk og hvor mye som selges på det åpne markedet. Smart 🙌🏻
p: Med solceller fra Eiik kan du se hva panelene produserer rett fra mobilen, og få tilgang til produksjonshistorikken din over tid.
h2: Se hvor mye strøm du produserer
p: Jeg vil anbefaler Eiik på det sterkeste. De har meget profesjonelle el-installatører og taktekkere/blikkenslagere som har utført en meget bra jobb på kort tid.”
p: “...Helt utrolig at 24 solcellepaneler kan produsere så mye strøm. Jeg bruker kun 50% av strømmen selv, resten selger jeg. Endelig er strømangsten borte.
next_texts: p: Vi leverer og monterer solcellepanel på store deler av østlandet.Ta kontakt med oss i dag for å se hvor mye du kan spare.

previous_texts: h2: Så enkelt er det å få solceller på taket

previous_texts: p: Don’t miss this opportunity to connect in person with like-minded professionals and become a more effective leader. Join us September 13th, 2022 for a morning dedicated to inspiring professionals, building lasting bonds, and creating real change.

p: This essential networking event will address this year’s theme of Leading in a Time of Change. You’ll be challenged to connect with peers, discover new insights, and grow as an authentic leader who can thrive in turbulent times and conquer your career challenges, whether you’re in the office, or in your living room.

p: The Women in Law Leadership Breakfast will bring together law firms and in-house legal professionals as part of an ongoing mission to advance gender equity and inspire a new generation of empowered professionals.

h2: Feel like having a baby isn’t as wonderful as it’s “supposed” to be?

p: Becoming a mother today feels more challenging than it has ever been. Yet, the narrative that goes along with this transition remains the same – being pregnant and having a baby is “wonderful” and “blissful” and “the best thing that will ever happen to you.” These messages that are seen all over social media, create a waterfall of “shoulds” and “supposed to’s” that cause many women to feel guilty, ashamed, and like a failure when they experience anything less. The real truth is – motherhood is messy. There are some good parts but also lots of overwhelming, frustrating, anxious, and sad parts too. At The Motherhood Center – we make space for it all.

p: Becoming a mother today feels more challenging than it has ever been. Yet, the narrative that goes along with this transition remains the same – being pregnant and having a baby is “wonderful” and “blissful” and “the best thing that will ever happen to you.” These messages that are seen all over social media, create a waterfall of “shoulds” and “supposed to’s” that cause many women to feel guilty, ashamed, and like a failure when they experience anything less. The real truth is – motherhood is messy. There are some good parts but also lots of overwhelming, frustrating, anxious, and sad parts too. At The Motherhood Center – we make space for it all.

p: 1 in 5 new and expecting mothers experience perinatal mood and anxiety disorders (PMADs). These conditions are incredibly common, yet many women are afraid to talk about how bad they are feeling due to the shame and stigma surrounding maternal mental health, or they don’t know where to go or who to turn to. PMADs include a number of different symptoms and diagnoses, including prenatal and postpartum anxiety, postpartum depression, postpartum OCD, postpartum PTSD, and postpartum psychosis. PMADs can strike at any time during pregnancy and up to one year postpartum. Despite the catch-all term “postpartum depression,” 50% of all PMAD cases develop during pregnancy. Here is some more information about PMADs:
p: Tragically, mental health issues including suicide are the leading cause of maternal mortality in New York City, and across the country.
h3: PMADs are the leading cause of maternal death in the U.S.
p: PMADs far exceed the rates of gestational diabetes, hypertension, and other conditions that affect pregnant women. Yet screening for PMADs is still not mandatory.

p: Tragically, mental health issues including suicide are the leading cause of maternal mortality in New York City, and across the country.
h3: Untreated PMADs can lead to adverse outcomes for mother and baby

p: If left untreated, PMADs can lead to adverse health and mental health outcomes for both mother and baby including pre-term labor, lower birth rate, limited bonding and attachment, and cognitive and developmental disorders.
next_texts: h2: What is the Perinatal Day Program?

p: The Motherhood Center has different levels of treatment to help you feel like yourself again. Our Day Program is a comprehensive level of care designed for new and expecting mothers/birthing people who are experiencing postpartum depression or other moderate to severe PMAD symptoms and having difficulty caring for themselves and/or their babies. The “magic” of the Day Program is that it helps perinatal people feel much BETTER – much FASTER.

p: Our outpatient treatment offerings include an initial evaluation, ongoing therapy with licensed perinatal mental health clinicians, ongoing medication management with reproductive psychiatrists, and trying-to-conceive consultations.

next_texts: p: “The PHP has been a trusted space where I felt very held and cared for. I came to the PHP feeling extremely desperate, anxious and scared and after one day I knew I had come to the right place. I felt a weight had been lifted as I was relieved because I knew I would get help here. Trust the doctors, trust the therapy and talk to your fellow cohort members. Healing is not a switch you can turn on and off, but you can learn how to exist and thrive in the in between. Thank you to The Motherhood Center!” – Day Program Graduate

p: “The Motherhood Center has saved my life. I was really struggling after having my son and the day program team really challenged me and helped me get better. The strategies and tools that I learned are not only beneficial for me postpartum, but these tools will be used for the rest of my life. I have felt so safe and taken care of here and I am eternally grateful for The Motherhood Center.” – Day Program Graduate

p: “This program has given me my life back. A new, more rich life with my son. I didn’t want to be in my life, I was trying to escape my reality, filled with regret. Now I have a life I could never imagine, with joy, excitement & connection with my son.” – Day Program Graduate
p: “I came in feeling rejected by my baby and unable to care for her or myself. I’m leaving whole, able to care for my baby, myself, get back to work even.” – Day Program Graduate

p: “When I first started the Day Program, I was suffering from radical mood swings and was frightened by the pattern of my thoughts. Being surrounded by like-minded women and a care team who were genuinely interested in helping has saved my life.” – Day Program Graduate

next_texts: p: Our outpatient treatment offerings include an initial evaluation, ongoing therapy with licensed perinatal mental health clinicians, ongoing medication management with reproductive psychiatrists, and trying-to-conceive consultations.
h4: Learn more about our outpatient treatment

p: No birth story or parenting journey is identical. That’s why The Motherhood Center strives to make all therapeutic services as accessible and accommodating as possible for parents of all identities and backgrounds. We acknowledge that not all pregnant people identify as women, and thus encourage LGBTQIA+ pregnant and postpartum people to seek clinical care with us and join our community. The Motherhood Center is a place to talk about the hard parts of parenting as they intersect with race, identity, gender, sexual orientation, and other important aspects of identity. Our commitment is to be an anti-racist / anti-oppressive organization. No matter how you identify, The Motherhood Center is here for you.

p: 
The Cannacares Dream Pod is formulated with specific terpenes to enhance the effectiveness of using the pod at night. Formulated with world class CBD the Dream pod helps you relax in a manner other CBD products cannot match.Many people have inadequate experiences when using CBD oil, but vaping can offer a more potent solution that enables you to experience the true power of CBD and full-spectrum hemp extracts.
p: 
360MG
h3: 
Dreams VapePod & Device
p: 
Cannacares CBD Capsules are made with high quality EU-GMP Certified CBD and MCT Coconut Oil is used as the carrier. The capsules are fast absorbing meaning that they work quickly and effectively. Each capsule is certified THC free and contains 30mg of CBD. We would suggest that 1 capsule is taken twice a day. The CBD capsules are available in units of 30 capsules and 60 capsules meaning that you get 750mg & 1500mg of CBD respectively.
p: 
30MG PER SERVING
next_texts:
h3: 
24hr CBD Patches
p: 
10MG & 20MG
p: 
Your body heat activates the patch and causes it to release a small amount of CBD through your skin and into your bloodstream. Think of it like an IV without the pesky needles. When you apply a transdermal CBD Patch to your skin, you set up a drug concentration gradient. That means the patch contains a lot of cannabinoid, while your skin does not. When a substance (like heat or CBD) is in high concentration, it naturally wants to spread out into the surrounding area. 
h3: 
Relief VapePod & Device
p: 
360MG
